{"tid":827748,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿叻爆擁橫店30億元酒店 曾志偉：好似佢俾貼士咁唔可信","createTime":"2018-09-19T07:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T10:11:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"26a3b18accf72cd05e0dc59b78ffef768f253ed2","tid":827748,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tk8Pj.XtYlAPmqHVhrQpgA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180919f072948.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Ftk8Pj.XtYlAPmqHVhrQpgA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180919f072948.jpg&h=45ee80c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】為電影《黃金兄弟》擔任監製兼演出的曾志偉出席首映禮時，談到執導的錢嘉樂笑指他任其拍攝，志偉謂：「唔係點啫！洗濕個頭，老闆睇過覺得ok！最重要出來效果如何？大家喜歡。拍了兩億幾，無諗過咁貴，自己都無拍過咁貴，但作為監製唔想導演有擔憂，好似縱兒子有乜就畀佢，所以同老闆吃飯時，仲問我地仲唔上契？」<br />\n<br />\n對於好友陳百祥(阿叻)指未有獲邀請出席首映禮，曾志偉表表示經已叮囑製片必定要親自致電阿叻。談到阿叻爆他於橫店擁市值30億元的酒店，志偉笑謂：「好似同佢畀貼士一樣不可信，如果我有仲使做咩！我都係打工仔，只是畀有少少股份，橫店拍戲成日都去住，買一、兩間可以住。」"},{"pid":"4a1c25ef7dc52b751427e073d4532d7f4d0e32dd","tid":827748,"uid":144063,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:03:29.000Z","msg":"死矮仔 扮撚晒野 屌你老母 又想浸收縮水?"},{"pid":"41c263daa5495aa6a06d6767144a1744f8ad200c","tid":827748,"uid":79355,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:19:53.000Z","msg":"所以話TVB封殺佢實係笑死人<br />\n佢駛撚係TVB撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7aa024a17a5e78c87593c92201b1f03846def0","tid":827748,"uid":17853,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"41c263daa5495aa6a06d6767144a1744f8ad200c","tid":827748,"uid":79355,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:19:53.000Z","msg":"所以話TVB封殺佢實係笑死人<br />\n佢駛撚係TVB撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited